title: Miranda Cartel - Divert - Synthpop Futurepop Dark Electro
description:
Miranda Cartel is a female-fronted dark electronic project. The sole member of the project is Arachna â€“ also known from her activities in the Lily of the Valley band.

While dark scene is rather egalitarian, it is still hard to find solo projects where a woman is responsible for both vocals and music production. Listening to Miranda Cartel we can only wish that more ladies take up synthesizers and DAW-s as well as microphones. The effects are both pleasing and professional.
